PLOS Musical Productions is proud to present the much loved classic, Miss Saigon in July 2016.

Would you like to be involved in bringing this classic story to the stage? The information night is a perfect opportunity to meet and greet the Production Team and the PLOS Family. 

This night is for those interested in auditioning or assisting backstage. You'll get to ask questions, be informed of the Production Team's vision for the show,and be one of the first to book your audition!

Attendance is not a requirement for involvement in production.

Audition details and Character synopsis can be found here: http://plos.asn.au/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Audition-Requirements-Miss-Saigon-Website-Final.pdf